<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hour-by-hour">hour by hour</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>时时刻刻地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Even if we ignore time, it's still going by, ticking away, second by second, minute by minute, hour by hour.
即使我们忽略时间，它仍然在流逝，一分一秒，时时刻刻，滴答地走着。</p><footer>2008 江苏改</footer></div></div>